  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will pilot test the intervention by randomizing 30 couples to one of three
      conditions: 1) DuoPACT, the newly-developed couples intervention; 2) Life Steps, a
      standardized antiretroviral adherence intervention for HIV+ individuals; and 3) a treatment
      as usual (TAU) assessment-only control condition. After randomization, intervention sessions
      will be delivered weekly (6 DuoPACT sessions, or 3 Life Steps sessions). All couples will be
      assessed pre/post intervention to evaluate intervention acceptability and feasibility.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
